title: Bump validators from 0.12.4 to 0.12.6 in /frontend

labels.name: dependencies
labels.description: Pull requests that update a dependency file

body:
Bumps [validators](https://github.com/kvesteri/validators) from 0.12.4 to 0.12.6.
Changelog *Sourced from [validators's changelog](https://github.com/kvesteri/validators/blob/master/CHANGES.rst).* > 0.12.6 (2019-05-08) > ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^ > > - Fixed domain validator for single character domains ([#118](https://github-redirect.dependabot.com/kvesteri/validators/issues/118), pull request courtesy kingbuzzman) > > > 0.12.5 (2019-04-15) > ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^ > > - Fixed py37 support ([#113](https://github-redirect.dependabot.com/kvesteri/validators/issues/113), pull request courtesy agiletechnologist)
Commits - See full diff in [compare view](https://github.com/kvesteri/validators/commits)
